{"tid":1747843,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"11月中巴士總載客量已破2億人次 巴士報站下月增20條巴士線載客量資訊","createTime":"2019-11-23T11:41:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T14:43:11.000Z","uid":297241,"like":60,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"a05d28be2743131e767d34728278c93b02c5690c","tid":1747843,"uid":297241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:41:00.000Z","msg":"11月中巴士總載客量已破2億人次 <br />\n巴士報站下月增20條巴士線載客量資訊<br />\n<br />\n交通諮詢委員會召開新一屆首次會議，會後交通事務局局長林衍新表示，當局會上匯報了2019年巴士服務的情況。其中直到11月16日，巴士總載客量已超過2億人次，估計今年全年的巴士載客量會超過2.3億人次，比去年超過1,500萬人次，增長約7％，而每日約有62萬人次乘搭巴士，當中有24條巴士路線每日有過萬人次使用。10月4日當天超過76.3萬人次搭巴士，創下歷史記錄。"},{"pid":"53c5cc9c8d5097163b90d7a59fdd1d09d486fcc0","tid":1747843,"uid":78377,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:51:32.000Z","msg":"以前就話火車地鐵快 方便<br />\n依家有都唔撚搭佢 <br />\n巴士加油<br />\n北區加路線呀屌你"},{"pid":"92b1856a1bcdd2901ed0bd7fb70dea75cfddabc5","tid":1747843,"uid":2404,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:56:24.000Z","msg":"行路都唔搭黨鐵"},{"pid":"cd7657564994b182925884daa2e5aa8b5a84aa92","tid":1747843,"uid":23087,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:56:45.000Z","msg":"坐地鐵好抑鬱<br />\n巴士更好"},{"pid":"6683f6c4a27066c0d28d955a9d3da056daf56f7b","tid":1747843,"uid":260036,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:57:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />黨鐵不了"},{"pid":"e8a67a2ed0f66c562f87b67fce2e9d6f386f1ecc","tid":1747843,"uid":34810,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:59:07.000Z","msg":"10月4個日做咩破左紀錄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b502cef875109d327e6c08c45df44bf839254f58","tid":1747843,"uid":9193,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e8a67a2ed0f66c562f87b67fce2e9d6f386f1ecc","tid":1747843,"uid":34810,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:59:07.000Z","msg":"10月4個日做咩破左紀錄<img src=\"