e":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T12:02:03.000Z","msg":"今日無巴士出旺角我行到去銘基書院都照搭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌佢老味"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T12:22:40.000Z","msg":"塘尾道咪有得坐囉 近馬會"},{"pid":"25b31b32aa83507a77191d99af29a9e98e685a43","tid":1747843,"uid":124711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T13:52:11.000Z","msg":"我都想有更多巴士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3da72b36bd658e76047f1df1514f8938df930dcb","tid":1747843,"uid":26602,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e8a67a2ed0f66c562f87b67fce2e9d6f386f1ecc","tid":1747843,"uid":34810,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:59:07.000Z","msg":"10月4個日做咩破左紀錄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T13:54:22.000Z","msg":"嗰晚党鐵大裝修7/8點開始封站，未夠十一點全線提早收皮"},{"pid":"b6fc925236e941ec1ec97d32732c2c41fb367bf9","tid":1747843,"uid":91771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T13:59:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.td.gov.hk/mini_site/atd/2018/tc/section5_t_1.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.td.gov.hk%2Fmini_site%2Fatd%2F2018%2Ftc%2Fsection5_t_1.html&d=SNVPshlwtiHAgFu1pF0TpNUsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=42eaa7d7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.td.gov.hk/mini_site/atd/2018/tc/section5_t_1.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>2017年的公共交通服務乘客量比2016年輕微上升約0.8%，至每日1,270萬人次。鐵路每日接載乘客550萬人次，乘客量比去年上升了2%，是乘客量最高的公共交通服務。載客量佔次位的是專營巴士服務，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">每日接載乘客397萬人次</span></span>，比去年上升0.2%。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港巴士載好多人咖<br />\n<br />\n呢單係澳門料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聽日只有一個目的<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">保蝗黨要輸！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"6d36917f0820b8b4c07a3dfc25cab07116b68a91","tid":1747843,"uid":288154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T14:13:18.000Z","msg":"11.24 民主歌聲獻香港 圍繞理大走一圈 【和理非行動post】<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k8yQUK2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk8yQUK2.png&h=727d0b17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n等候時及面對<span style=\"color: red;\">白警</span>時唱<strong>《Sing Hallelujah To The Lord》</strong><br />\n<br />\n香港區 6:00pm 灣仔紅隧入口集合，大量兩層巴士接過紅隧，或自行行過紅隧。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【急】請傳給撞區候選人！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n必在 11月 24日 7:30am 前，在facebook發表，證明已為<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">7－11pm</span></strong>活動申請不反通知書，先發表就出線有票，遲發表要退選。</span><br />\n撞區表 <a href=\"https://hkfactcheck.io/crashes/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkfactcheck.io%2Fcrashes%2F1&d=SNVPshlwtiHAgFu1pF0TpNUsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=94e8bed6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkfactcheck.io/crashes/1</a><br />\n<br />\n誠邀：曾出席『<span style=\"color: red;\">民主歌聲獻中華</span>』演藝人、所有民主派議員、及候選人。〔民主派即是所有推動民主，包括本土及泛民〕<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span><br />\n<br />\n11.24 民主歌聲獻香港 圍繞理大走一圈 【和理非行動post】<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1747254\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1747254</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">幫幫手推一推行動post拉！連登重有邊個唔去投票！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n下期預告：12.1 民主歌聲撐林夕 圍繞理大走一圈 【行動post】"},{"pid":"017c58d76f4ba1b4f9425165b6f168556f54b190","tid":1747843,"uid":157508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T14:13:23.000Z","msg":"澳聞嚟嘅屌你"}]}